<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Aaladen Enabottle<Brell></font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-08-26 08:05:01</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Hello fello mages, I must say this is the best robe for a mage to wear, I have one myself, I was lucky enuff to obtain it on my first trip to PoH. I was offered a very very large sum of money to give up my looting rights to this robe *sigh* but I declined. I wouldnt sell the looting rights for it for all the money in the lands of Norrath, I would much rather have a robe that not everyone and there sister has like SMR and seeing how its NO DROP it makes it even better, I have only seen 5 or 6 others with an Apothic robe on Brell. But needless to say this robe draws attention, I have to take it off everytime i go into newbie land or i get jumped my the newbies asking me what robe is that, where can i get one, yada yada yada, Its not that i dont mind answering newbies questions...but damn when yer trying to get something done getting jumped by a mob of newbies cause of yer wardrobe starts to suck after awhile. hehe Anyway, good luck to you fellow mages that seek this robe, remember patients is a virtue, it will come to you sooner or later.<BR>
<BR>
Aaladen Enabottle Order of Shadows<BR>
Lvl 52 mage of Brell</font></td></tr></table>
